    "description": "Adapted from the HW11 Contacts API Postman collection for HW13.\n\nDefault base_url points to the Render deployment.\nRecommended manual flow:\n1. Register user with a real email.\n2. Open the confirmation email, copy the token from the link, paste it into verify_token.\n3. Run Confirm email by token.\n4. Run Login. The collection stores access_token and refresh_token automatically.\n5. Run protected users/contacts requests.\n\nFor password reset, run Request password reset, copy the token from the email link into reset_token, then run Confirm password reset.",
